# Binary Search Visualizer

Here's a complete, self-contained HTML file with a clean, interactive binary search visualization:

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Binary Search Visualizer</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 50%, #0f3460 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            color: #e0e0e0;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00d2ff, #7b2ff7);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .subtitle {
            color: #8892b0;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 28px;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 860px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        /* ── Controls ── */
        .controls {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 14px;
            align-items: flex-end;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .control-group {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        .control-group label {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #8892b0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        }

        input[type="number"], input[type="text"] {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 8px;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            padding: 10px 14px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            width: 180px;
            outline: none;
            transition: border-color 0.2s;
        }

        input[type="number"]:focus, input[type="text"]:focus {
            border-color: #00d2ff;
        }

        button {
            padding: 10px 22px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.1s, opacity 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        }

        button:active { transform: scale(0.96); }

        button:disabled {
            opacity: 0.35;
            cursor: not-allowed;
            transform: none;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d2ff, #7b2ff7);
            color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover:not(:disabled) {
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.5);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            color: #e0e0e0;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover:not(:disabled) {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
        }

        .btn-step {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f7971e, #ffd200);
            color: #1a1a2e;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 210, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-step:hover:not(:disabled) {
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(255, 210, 0, 0.5);
        }

        /* ── Array display ── */
        .array-section {
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .array-label {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #8892b0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
        }

        .array-wrapper {
            overflow-x: auto;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .array-container {
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
            min-width: max-content;
            padding: 10px 4px;
        }

        .box-wrapper {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 5px;
        }

        .box {
            width: 54px;
            height: 54px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
            color: #c0c8e0;
            transition: all 0.35s ease;
            position: relative;
        }

        .box-index {
            font-size: 0.68rem;
            color: #555e7a;
        }

        /* State classes */
        .box.in-range {
            border-color: rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.5);
            background: rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.1);
            color: #e0f7ff;
        }

        .box.mid {
            border-color: #ffd200;
            background: rgba(255, 210, 0, 0.2);
            color: #fff8cc;
            box-shadow: 0 0 14px rgba(255, 210, 0, 0.5);
            transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.08);
        }

        .box.out-of-range {
            opacity: 0.25;
            border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
        }

        .box.found {
            border-color: #00ff88;
            background: rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.2);
            color: #ccffe8;
            box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.6);
            transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.12);
        }

        .box.not-found-range {
            opacity: 0.2;
        }

        /* Pointer labels */
        .pointer-row {
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
            min-width: max-content;
            padding: 0 4px;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        .pointer-cell {
            width: 54px;
            height: 22px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 2px;
            font-size: 0.65rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.03em;
        }

        .ptr-lo  { color: #00d2ff; }
        .ptr-hi  { color: #ff6b9d; }
        .ptr-mid { color: #ffd200; }

        /* ── Log ── */
        .log-section { margin-top: 6px; }

        .log-title {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #8892b0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .log-box {
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
            padding: 14px 16px;
            min-height: 80px;
            max-height: 220px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .log-entry { display: flex; gap: 10px; }
        .log-step  { color: #555e7a; min-width: 24px; }
        .log-text  { color: #b0bec5; }
        .log-text.highlight { color: #ffd200; }
        .log-text.success   { color: #00ff88; }
        .log-text.fail      { color: #ff6b9d; }
        .log-text.info      { color: #00d2ff; }

        /* ── Result banner ── */
        .result-banner {
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 14px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: none;
            margin-top: 14px;
            animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease;
        }

        .result-banner.found-banner {
            background: rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.15);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.4);
            color: #00ff88;
            display: block;
        }

        .result-banner.not-found-banner {
            background: rgba(255, 107, 157, 0.15);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 107, 157, 0.4);
            color: #ff6b9d;
            display: block;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(6px); }
            to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        /* ── Legend ── */
        .legend {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 16px;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 16px;
        }

        .legend-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 7px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #8892b0;
        }

        .legend-dot {
            width: 14px;
            height: 14px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            border: 2px solid;
        }

        .dot-range   { border-color: rgba(0,210,255,0.7);  background: rgba(0,210,255,0.15); }
        .dot-mid     { border-color: #ffd200;               background: rgba(255,210,0,0.2);  }
        .dot-found   { border-color: #00ff88;               background: rgba(0,255,136,0.2);  }
        .dot-out     { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); opacity:0.5; }

        /* ── Scrollbar ── */
        ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; height: 6px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: transparent; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-radius: 3px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>Binary Search Visualizer</h1>
<p class="subtitle">Step through the algorithm and watch it divide and conquer</p>

<!-- Controls Card -->
<div class="card">
    <div class="controls">
        <div class="control-group">
            <label>Sorted Array (comma-separated)</label>
            <input type="text" id="arrayInput"
                   value="3, 7, 12, 18, 24, 31, 45, 56, 63, 77, 84, 95"
                   placeholder="e.g. 1, 5, 9, 14, 22">
        </div>
        <div class="control-group">
            <label>Target Value</label>
            <input type="number" id="targetInput" value="45" placeholder="e.g. 45">
        </div>
        <div class="control-group">
            <label>&nbsp;</label>
            <button class="btn-primary" onclick="initSearch()">▶ Start</button>
        </div>
        <div class="control-group">
            <label>&nbsp;</label>
            <button class="btn-step" id="stepBtn" onclick="step()" disabled>⏭ Next Step</button>
        </div>
        <div class="control-group">
            <label>&nbsp;</label>
            <button class="btn-secondary" onclick="resetAll()">↺ Reset</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Legend -->
    <div class="legend">
        <div class="legend-item">
            <div class="legend-dot dot-range"></div> Search Range
        </div>
        <div class="legend-item">
            <div class="legend-dot dot-mid"></div> Mid Element
        </div>
        <div class="legend-item">
            <div class="legend-dot dot-found"></div> Found
        </div>
        <div class="legend-item">
            <div class="legend-dot dot-out"></div> Eliminated
        </div>
        <div class="legend-item">
            <span style="color:#00d2ff; font-weight:700; font-size:0.85rem;">LO</span>&nbsp;Low Pointer
        </div>
        <div class="legend-item">
            <span style="color:#ffd200; font-weight:700; font-size:0.85rem;">MID</span>&nbsp;Mid Pointer
        </div>
        <div class="legend-item">
            <span style="color:#ff6b9d; font-weight:700; font-size:0.85rem;">HI</span>&nbsp;High Pointer
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Array Visualization Card -->
<div class="card">
    <div class="array-section">
        <div class="array-label">Array</div>
        <div class="array-wrapper">
            <div class="array-container" id="arrayContainer"></div>
            <div class="pointer-row" id="pointerRow"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="resultBanner" class="result-banner"></div>
</div>

<!-- Log Card -->
<div class="card log-section">
    <div class="log-title">Step Log</div>
    <div class="log-box" id="logBox">
        <div class="log-entry">
            <span class="log-step">—</span>
            <span class="log-text info">Enter an array and target, then press ▶ Start.</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script>
    // ── State ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
    let arr       = [];
    let target    = null;
    let lo        = 0;
    let hi        = 0;
    let stepCount = 0;
    let done      = false;

    // ── Helpers ────────────────────────────────────────────────
    function parseArray(str) {
        return str.split(',')
                  .map(s => parseInt(s.trim(), 10))
                  .filter(n => !isNaN(n));
    }

    function isSorted(a) {
        for (let i = 1; i < a.length; i++) {
            if (a[i] < a[i - 1]) return false;
        }
        return true;
    }

    function addLog(stepNum, text, cls = '') {
        const box   = document.getElementById('logBox');
        const entry = document.createElement('div');
        entry.className = 'log-entry';
        entry.innerHTML = `<span class="log-step">${stepNum}.</span>
                           <span class="log-text ${cls}">${text}</span>`;
        box.appendChild(entry);
        box.scrollTop = box.scrollHeight;
    }

    // ── Render array boxes ─────────────────────────────────────
    function renderArray(midIndex = -1, foundIndex = -1) {
        const container  = document.getElementById('arrayContainer');
        const pointerRow = document.getElementById('pointerRow');
        container.innerHTML  = '';
        pointerRow.innerHTML = '';

        arr.forEach((val, i) => {
            // Box
            const wrapper = document.createElement('div');
            wrapper.className = 'box-wrapper';

            const box = document.createElement('div');
            box.className = 'box';
            box.id = `box-${i}`;
            box.textContent = val;

            if (foundIndex !== -1) {
                box.classList.add(i === foundIndex ? 'found' : 'not-found-range');
            } else if (!done) {
                if (i < lo || i > hi)        box.classList.add('out-of-range');
                else if (i === midIndex)      box.classList.add('mid');
                else                          box.classList.add('in-range');
            }

            const idx = document.createElement('div');
            idx.className = 'box-index';
            idx.textContent = i;

            wrapper.appendChild(box);
            wrapper.appendChild(idx);
            container.appendChild(wrapper);

            // Pointer cell
            const cell = document.createElement('div');
            cell.className = 'pointer-cell';

            const labels = [];
            if (!done || foundIndex !== -1) {
                if (i === lo  && foundIndex === -1) labels.push(`<span class="ptr-lo">LO</span>`);
                if (i === hi  && foundIndex === -1) labels.push(`<span class="ptr-hi">HI</span>`);
                if (i === midIndex && foundIndex === -1) labels.push(`<span class="ptr-mid">MID</span>`);
            }
            cell.innerHTML = labels.join(' ');
            pointerRow.appendChild(cell);
        });
    }

    // ── Init ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
    function initSearch() {
        const rawArr = document.getElementById('arrayInput').value;
        const rawTgt = document.getElementById('targetInput').value;

        arr    = parseArray(rawArr);
        target = parseInt(rawTgt, 10);

        // Validations
        if (arr.length === 0) {
            alert('Please enter a valid array of numbers.');
            return;
        }
        if (!isSorted(arr)) {
            alert('Array must be sorted in ascending order!');
            return;
        }
        if (isNaN(target)) {
            alert('Please enter a valid target number.');
            return;
        }

        lo        = 0;
        hi        = arr.length - 1;
        stepCount = 0;
        done      = false;

        document.getElementById('stepBtn').disabled    = false;
        document.getElementById('resultBanner').className = 'result-banner';
        document.getElementById('resultBanner').textContent = '';

        // Clear log
        const logBox = document.getElementById('logBox');
        logBox.innerHTML = '';
        addLog('→', `Array: [${arr.join(', ')}]`, 'info');
        addLog('→', `Target: <strong>${target}</strong> | Indices 0 – ${arr.length - 1}`, 'info');

        renderArray();
    }

    // ── Step ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
    function step() {
        if (done) return;
        stepCount++;

        if (lo > hi) {
            // Not found
            finishNotFound();
            return;
        }

        const mid    = Math.floor((lo + hi) / 2);
        const midVal = arr[mid];

        addLog(stepCount,
            `lo=${lo}, hi=${hi} → mid=${mid} (value <strong>${midVal}</strong>)`,
            'highlight');

        if (midVal === target) {
            // Found!
            addLog(stepCount,
                `🎉 arr[${mid}] = ${midVal} === target ${target}. Found at index ${mid}!`,
                'success');
            renderArray(-1, mid);
            showBanner(true, mid);
            done = true;
            document.getElementById('stepBtn').disabled = true;
            return;
        }

        if (midVal < target) {
            addLog(stepCount,
                `arr[${mid}]=${midVal} < ${target} → search right half (lo = ${mid + 1})`,
                'info');
            renderArray(mid);
            lo = mid + 1;
        } else {
            addLog(stepCount,
                `arr[${mid}]=${midVal} > ${target} → search left half (hi = ${mid - 1})`,
                'info');
            renderArray(mid);
            hi = mid - 1;
        }

        // After updating, check if exhausted
        if (lo > hi) {
            stepCount++;
            finishNotFound();
        }
    }

    function finishNotFound() {
        addLog(stepCount, `lo (${lo}) > hi (${hi}): search space exhausted.`, 'fail');
        addLog(stepCount, `✗ Target ${target} not found in array.`, 'fail');
        renderArray();
        showBanner(false, -1);
        done = true;
        document.getElementById('stepBtn').disabled = true;
    }

    function showBanner(found, index) {
        const banner = document.getElementById('resultBanner');
        if (found) {
            banner.className   = 'result-banner found-banner';
            banner.textContent = `✅ Found ${target} at index ${index}!`;
        } else {
            banner.className   = 'result-banner not-found-banner';
            banner.textContent = `❌ ${target} is not in the array.`;
        }
    }

    // ── Reset ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
    function resetAll() {
        arr       = [];
        target    = null;
        lo = hi   = 0;
        stepCount = 0;
        done      = false;

        document.getElementById('arrayContainer').innerHTML  = '';
        document.getElementById('pointerRow').innerHTML      = '';
        document.getElementById('resultBanner').className    = 'result-banner';
        document.getElementById('resultBanner').textContent  = '';
        document.getElementById('stepBtn').disabled          = true;

        const logBox = document.getElementById('logBox');
        logBox.innerHTML = '';
        addLog('—', 'Enter an array and target, then press ▶ Start.', 'info');
    }

    // ── Init on load ───────────────────────────────────────────
    window.onload = () => {
        resetAll();
        // Pre-render the default array for a nice first impression
        arr    = parseArray(document.getElementById('arrayInput').value);
        target = parseInt(document.getElementById('targetInput').value, 10);
        lo     = 0;
        hi     = arr.length - 1;
        renderArray();
    };
</script>
</body>
</html>
```

---

## What's included

| Feature | Detail |
|---|---|
| **Array input** | Editable comma-separated list — defaults to 12 sorted numbers |
| **Target input** | Any integer you want to search for |
| **▶ Start** | Parses & validates the array (must be sorted), resets state |
| **⏭ Next Step** | Advances one iteration, updates all visuals & log |
| **↺ Reset** | Clears everything back to blank |
| **Box colors** | Blue = search range · Gold = mid · Green = found · Faded = eliminated |
| **Pointer labels** | `LO`, `MID`, `HI` float beneath the relevant boxes each step |
| **Step log** | Scrollable history showing exact comparisons and decisions |
| **Result banner** | Green "Found at index N" or red "Not found" at the end |

Just save it as **`binary-search.html`** and open it in any browser — no dependencies needed!

